Package de.presti.ree6.sql

Record Class SQLWorker

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.presti.ree6.sql.SQLWorker
Record Components:
sqlConnector - an Instance of the SQL-Connector to retrieve the data from.
public record SQLWorker(SQLConnector sqlConnector) extends Record
A Class to actually handle the SQL data. Used to provide Data from the Database and to save Data into the Database.

Constructor to create a new Instance of the SQLWorker with a ref to the SQL-Connector.
